WEBVTT

03:25.520 --> 03:26.280
You're leaving just like that.

03:26.280 --> 03:27.120
It's always like this.

03:27.120 --> 03:28.579
You never tell me earlier.

03:28.960 --> 03:30.600
Make sure you keep those US dollars safe.

03:30.600 --> 03:31.760
Where are the US dollars in the safe?

03:31.760 --> 03:32.620
I took them all.

03:33.079 --> 03:34.079
When you get there,

03:34.079 --> 03:35.320
we'll keep in touch anytime.

03:35.320 --> 03:37.160
Let me know you're safe when you arrive.

03:37.160 --> 03:38.040
Call me anytime.

03:38.040 --> 03:38.960
Fengnian.

03:47.160 --> 03:48.160
Yunkui.

03:48.840 --> 03:50.040
You're really alive.

03:56.560 --> 03:57.560
I'm alive.

04:01.480 --> 04:02.610
I heard from Yujiao.

04:05.000 --> 04:06.660
I need to talk to Yunkui alone.

04:06.960 --> 04:07.680
You go first,

04:07.680 --> 04:09.680
and have them come back to pick me up.

04:09.720 --> 04:10.720
Okay.

04:13.120 --> 04:13.920
Yunkui.

04:14.360 --> 04:15.960
It's good that you're alive.

04:16.000 --> 04:17.600
It's good that you're alive.

04:17.839 --> 04:18.720
I'll get going.

04:27.960 --> 04:28.480
Here.

04:28.920 --> 04:30.160
Ma'am, let me take it.

04:30.920 --> 04:32.240
The commander told us to go first.

04:32.240 --> 04:33.840
We'll arrange a car to pick him up later.

04:33.840 --> 04:35.000
Yes.

04:55.200 --> 04:56.440
Still alive.

04:56.840 --> 04:57.800
Alive.

04:57.840 --> 04:59.000
You're so bold.

04:59.560 --> 05:01.480
You dare to return to Nanjing at this time.

05:01.480 --> 05:02.680
Nanjing is tense right now.

05:02.680 --> 05:04.160
There are military police and spies everywhere.

05:04.160 --> 05:05.890
Sun Huaiyi's men are also here.

05:05.920 --> 05:07.080
If anyone spots you,

05:07.080 --> 05:08.000
it's a dead end.

05:08.160 --> 05:09.020
I'm not afraid.

05:09.200 --> 05:10.520
I'm waiting for him to arrest me.

05:10.520 --> 05:12.650
I'm going to confront him face to face.

05:12.720 --> 05:13.360
Confront?

05:13.960 --> 05:15.360
Who are you confronting?

05:16.200 --> 05:18.060
This is an extraordinary period.

05:18.080 --> 05:18.480
You,

05:18.600 --> 05:20.520
are a definite runaway general.

05:21.000 --> 05:22.600
No need for a court-martial,

05:22.640 --> 05:23.520
or a trial.

05:24.160 --> 05:26.160
Sun Huaiyi can execute you anytime.

05:26.360 --> 05:27.280
I don't get it.

05:28.120 --> 05:29.160
I argued with him,

05:29.880 --> 05:31.480
but does he hate me that much?

05:36.600 --> 05:38.640
Sun Huaiyi's command was conservative.

05:38.640 --> 05:40.840
The 187th Division suffered heavy losses.

05:40.840 --> 05:43.370
Someone has to take responsibility for this.

05:43.600 --> 05:45.040
If Sun Huaiyi takes it,

05:45.200 --> 05:47.530
the 187th Division might be deactivated.

05:48.159 --> 05:49.620
If a subordinate takes it,

05:49.760 --> 05:52.080
the 187th Division might regroup.

05:52.640 --> 05:53.570
But at that time,

05:54.640 --> 05:56.360
everyone thought you died for the country.

05:56.360 --> 05:58.600
So Sun Huaiyi put the blame on you.

05:59.000 --> 06:00.120
That must be it.

06:06.800 --> 06:08.880
The runaway general is to blame.

06:09.640 --> 06:11.040
Is that what you mean too?

06:12.400 --> 06:13.560
Is it?

06:19.480 --> 06:21.340
For a soldier on the battlefield,

06:22.360 --> 06:23.890
what's the biggest insult?

06:27.400 --> 06:28.160
A deserter.

06:32.480 --> 06:33.400
Tell me,

06:33.720 --> 06:35.640
am I a deserter?

06:37.080 --> 06:38.080
Yunkui.

06:39.040 --> 06:41.170
We've been brothers for so many years.

06:41.800 --> 06:43.680
How do you think I see you?

06:50.880 --> 06:52.000
On November 6th,

06:52.360 --> 06:53.560
I went to Commander Luo.

06:53.560 --> 06:55.360
I told him everything I knew.

06:56.040 --> 06:57.600
He only answered me three words.

06:57.600 --> 06:58.600
I know.

06:59.240 --> 07:00.360
On November 8th,

07:00.360 --> 07:02.360
I stopped Commander Chen in the dining hall.

07:02.360 --> 07:03.160
Before I could even speak,

07:03.160 --> 07:03.920
he said,

07:03.920 --> 07:04.840
'Say no more.

07:05.000 --> 07:06.560
I know what you are going to say.'

07:06.560 --> 07:07.640
It's always the same.

07:07.640 --> 07:09.200
Say no more. I know.

07:09.720 --> 07:11.080
They know everything,

07:11.560 --> 07:13.890
but no one wants to bring it out in the open.

07:18.480 --> 07:19.840
Ultimately,

07:21.000 --> 07:23.460
Sun Huaiyi didn't treat you as one of his own.

07:24.520 --> 07:25.800
One of his own?

07:26.680 --> 07:28.810
Were those 6,000 brothers not his own?

07:29.280 --> 07:30.200
Did they just let them

07:30.200 --> 07:32.130
become cannon fodder for nothing?

07:32.480 --> 07:33.409
This is not over.

07:34.280 --> 07:35.040
I will either go to Minister He,

07:35.040 --> 07:36.360
or I will go to the Chairman.

07:36.360 --> 07:37.159
Are you crazy?

07:38.000 --> 07:38.400
Well,

07:38.560 --> 07:39.800
Are we closer to the Chairman,

07:39.800 --> 07:41.080
or is Sun Huaiyi

07:41.080 --> 07:41.880
closer to him?

07:42.360 --> 07:44.200
The Battle of Shanghai just ended.

07:44.200 --> 07:46.560
The direct line troops lost seventy or eighty percent.

07:46.560 --> 07:47.480
Nanjing needs to be defended.

07:47.480 --> 07:48.840
China needs to be defended.

07:48.840 --> 07:50.400
Those warlords need to be guarded against.

07:50.400 --> 07:52.200
Would the Chairman clip his own wings at this time

07:52.200 --> 07:53.800
and investigate Sun Huaiyi?

07:54.040 --> 07:55.240
Think about it carefully.

07:55.240 --> 07:56.560
You want justice?

07:56.840 --> 07:58.400
You surviving

07:58.600 --> 08:00.640
is the greatest justice.

08:02.760 --> 08:03.840
With the enemy at the gates,

08:03.840 --> 08:06.360
do we really need to argue about right and wrong?

08:06.360 --> 08:07.520
Things will work out in time.

08:07.520 --> 08:08.520
Work out?

08:09.560 --> 08:10.120
Can you even cover up

08:10.120 --> 08:11.680
the lies you told yourselves?

08:11.680 --> 08:13.080
Where did the 159th Division go?

08:13.080 --> 08:15.440
My brothers were defending Baijiazhai to the death!

08:15.440 --> 08:16.160
If we joined forces,

08:16.160 --> 08:18.240
we could have won that battle, you know?

08:18.240 --> 08:19.040
And you?

08:19.040 --> 08:19.640
You retreated at the last minute,

08:19.640 --> 08:21.480
making my soldiers look like deserters.

08:21.480 --> 08:22.600
Is that fair?

08:23.640 --> 08:25.080
Is it?

08:25.960 --> 08:27.640
What's the point of saying this now?

08:27.640 --> 08:28.440
It has a point.

08:28.720 --> 08:29.580
I'm asking you,

08:29.800 --> 08:31.800
who gave the order to retreat from Liuzhen?

08:31.800 --> 08:32.730
I can't tell you.

08:32.799 --> 08:33.360
Answer me.

08:33.360 --> 08:34.960
I can't tell you.

08:38.600 --> 08:39.320
Yunkui,

08:40.240 --> 08:41.370
I have a suggestion.

08:41.640 --> 08:42.700
I'll go find Dai Li.

08:43.039 --> 08:43.970
I can talk to him.

08:44.520 --> 08:45.360
If he helps,

08:45.760 --> 08:48.400
he will speak up for you to the Chairman.

08:49.080 --> 08:50.610
Then you will have a chance.

08:50.720 --> 08:52.720
Sun Huaiyi is the best at seeing which way the wind blows.

08:52.720 --> 08:53.720
When the time comes, he will naturally

08:53.720 --> 08:55.980
help cover up your battlefield affairs.

08:56.360 --> 08:57.090
At that time,

08:57.240 --> 08:58.960
whether you want to mend your relationship with him

08:58.960 --> 09:00.160
or get revenge on him,

09:00.200 --> 09:01.560
it's up to you.

09:08.000 --> 09:09.330
The old man and your wife

09:09.880 --> 09:11.540
are probably almost in Wuhan.

09:11.640 --> 09:12.920
I asked someone to get them three

09:12.920 --> 09:14.180
boat tickets to Wuhan.

09:15.480 --> 09:16.760
Thank you.

09:19.200 --> 09:20.860
You know the old man's temper.

09:21.000 --> 09:22.920
He was furious when he heard about your accident.

09:22.920 --> 09:24.980
It took a lot to persuade him to leave.

09:25.120 --> 09:26.000
Did my dad...

09:26.000 --> 09:26.720
Alright,

09:26.720 --> 09:27.520
stop talking.

09:28.560 --> 09:30.220
Take these US dollars for now.

09:30.320 --> 09:31.320
No.

09:34.600 --> 09:35.760
Hurry to Wuhan

09:36.080 --> 09:37.680
and meet up with your family.

09:39.000 --> 09:39.880
With the clothes you are wearing,

09:39.880 --> 09:41.720
you'll be caught as soon as you step out.

09:41.720 --> 09:43.400
Come, go upstairs with me to change.

09:43.400 --> 09:44.640
Can Nanjing be held?

09:51.680 --> 09:52.610
What do you mean?

09:52.840 --> 09:54.120
I know the rest of my division

09:54.120 --> 09:56.120
was ordered to retreat to Mufu Mountain.

09:56.120 --> 09:57.000
I can temporarily put aside

09:57.000 --> 09:58.800
all my disputes with Sun Huaiyi.

09:58.960 --> 10:00.360
I want to defend Nanjing.

10:00.600 --> 10:01.800
It's not that simple.

10:02.600 --> 10:03.320
You,

10:03.320 --> 10:04.560
hurry and send a telegram to the old man

10:04.560 --> 10:05.620
to say you're safe.

10:13.920 --> 10:15.160
I'll go get it for you.

11:30.000 --> 11:31.960
There! Stop!

11:42.280 --> 11:43.610
Stop looking, let's go.

11:49.680 --> 11:51.320
Come with us.

12:28.280 --> 12:29.720
Keep order.

12:30.000 --> 12:30.360
Watch out.

12:30.360 --> 12:31.040
Slow down.

12:31.200 --> 12:32.240
Keep order.

12:32.440 --> 12:34.080
Be safe.

12:34.320 --> 12:35.360
Watch out for the kids.

12:35.360 --> 12:36.120
Slow down.

12:37.080 --> 12:38.240
Slow down.

12:39.440 --> 12:40.320
Oh my goodness.

12:40.520 --> 12:41.120
Watch out for the elderly and children.

12:41.120 --> 12:42.680
Taking this boat is killing me.

12:42.680 --> 12:43.240
Stop swaying, Mrs. Liu.

12:43.240 --> 12:45.160
My legs don't feel like mine anymore.

12:45.160 --> 12:45.720
I'm not swaying.

12:45.720 --> 12:46.520
Stop swaying.

12:46.800 --> 12:48.530
You're the one swaying, ma'am.

12:55.040 --> 12:56.880
Quick, sit down.

12:59.120 --> 13:00.920
How did Shanghai turn into this?

13:01.400 --> 13:02.080
Master,

13:02.280 --> 13:03.340
Shanghai is so big,

13:03.440 --> 13:04.640
where are we heading?

13:04.880 --> 13:07.200
No. 8 Jurenli, French Concession.

13:07.560 --> 13:08.760
We have a house there,

13:08.920 --> 13:09.800
understand?

13:12.800 --> 13:13.800
Hello, excuse me,

13:13.960 --> 13:15.840
how do we get to the French Concession?

13:15.840 --> 13:17.000
Walk ahead for three miles,

13:17.000 --> 13:18.560
and you'll reach the French Concession.

13:18.560 --> 13:19.560
Thank you.

13:20.680 --> 13:21.940
Let's go, three miles.

13:22.440 --> 13:23.200
Wait,

13:23.720 --> 13:25.180
Ma'am is not feeling well.

13:25.280 --> 13:27.760
Wanfu, hurry and call a rickshaw.

13:28.040 --> 13:28.700
Go quickly.

13:30.840 --> 13:31.640
Slow down.

13:32.240 --> 13:33.160
Slow down.

13:36.360 --> 13:37.640
Go quickly.

13:38.280 --> 13:40.280
Master, how do I call one?

13:40.800 --> 13:41.640
Call one!

13:41.880 --> 13:43.640
I yelled but they won't come.

13:44.960 --> 13:45.760
Master.

13:46.960 --> 13:47.800
Ma'am.

13:49.160 --> 13:50.240
Slow down.

14:05.920 --> 14:06.680
Go quickly.

14:12.360 --> 14:14.160
Master, come sit.

14:16.920 --> 14:17.280
Master.

14:17.280 --> 14:17.800
Dad.

14:17.840 --> 14:18.960
Be careful.

14:36.560 --> 14:37.400
Rickshaw! Rickshaw!

14:37.400 --> 14:38.600
Let's go. To the pier.

14:38.800 --> 14:40.040
I'm not taking passengers.

14:40.040 --> 14:41.280
No, please, brother, help me out.

14:41.280 --> 14:42.940
My wife is about to give birth.

14:43.160 --> 14:44.400
I'm in a hurry to pick someone up.

14:44.400 --> 14:45.160
How about this.

14:45.160 --> 14:46.760
I'll give you one dollar, okay?

14:46.760 --> 14:47.440
One dollar?

14:47.600 --> 14:49.120
You obviously don't know the market rate.

14:49.120 --> 14:50.720
The starting fare is three dollars now.

14:50.720 --> 14:51.480
Let go.

14:51.840 --> 14:52.800
Little punk.

14:53.120 --> 14:54.560
You're obsessed with money.

14:54.560 --> 14:55.920
Why are you having a baby now?

14:55.920 --> 14:57.400
Tell your kid to wait a bit longer.

14:57.400 --> 15:00.000
You won't earn three dollars in your lifetime.

15:05.200 --> 15:06.320
Make way.

15:07.760 --> 15:08.920
Make way.

15:09.640 --> 15:10.760
Make way.

15:23.360 --> 15:24.480
Thank you.

15:24.640 --> 15:25.760
You're welcome.

15:31.920 --> 15:32.800
Thank you.

15:33.320 --> 15:34.360
You're welcome.

16:04.240 --> 16:05.370
Stop! My cart! Stop!

16:05.400 --> 16:06.800
The money is on the goods.

16:13.640 --> 16:14.840
What kind of person is this?

16:14.840 --> 16:17.170
You should have told me you were buying it.

16:25.080 --> 16:27.010
Where did you get this broken cart?

16:27.200 --> 16:28.160
It's wobbling side to side.

16:28.160 --> 16:29.690
It's like selling piglets.

16:30.200 --> 16:32.160
Ma'am, I didn't mean it.

16:32.680 --> 16:33.560
Sit tight.

16:33.960 --> 16:35.880
If you think it's broken, go get one yourself.

16:35.880 --> 16:37.560
I was almost beaten to death.

16:38.560 --> 16:40.020
You didn't rent this cart?

16:40.520 --> 16:41.320
Watch out for the bump!

16:41.320 --> 16:42.160
Slow down.

16:42.440 --> 16:43.440
Wait.

16:43.800 --> 16:45.560
Did you say this cart was stolen?

16:45.560 --> 16:47.490
How could I have stolen it, Master?

16:47.560 --> 16:48.760
The money you gave me,

16:48.760 --> 16:50.880
I spent it all on this cart.

16:51.120 --> 16:53.880
Taking without asking is stealing.

16:54.480 --> 16:55.880
I won't ride in this cart.

16:56.320 --> 16:56.920
Slow down.

16:57.080 --> 16:58.210
Ma'am, are you okay?

16:59.840 --> 17:02.160
Master, look at the situation now.

17:02.800 --> 17:04.060
The madam is pregnant.

17:04.119 --> 17:05.920
Having a broken cart is better than nothing.

17:05.920 --> 17:06.560
Right?

17:06.839 --> 17:08.240
Get in quickly, let's go.

17:08.440 --> 17:09.369
Then you ride it.

17:09.680 --> 17:10.560
I can't ride it.

17:10.640 --> 17:12.760
I can't sit on the same level as the madam.

17:12.760 --> 17:13.560
Please get in.

17:13.680 --> 17:14.440
You sit.

17:14.680 --> 17:15.680
I won't.

17:16.079 --> 17:17.160
Please get in, let's go.

17:17.160 --> 17:18.890
If he tells you to sit, just sit.

17:19.040 --> 17:20.160
You are like a dead weight.

17:20.160 --> 17:21.480
Why are you being so modest?

17:21.480 --> 17:22.810
You're the dead weight.

17:23.280 --> 17:24.119
Father.

17:25.079 --> 17:26.480
I'll walk with you.

17:27.440 --> 17:28.200
Sitting is

17:29.000 --> 17:30.930
more uncomfortable than walking.

17:31.280 --> 17:32.600
Wanfu is also tired.

17:34.360 --> 17:35.560
Alright.

17:36.720 --> 17:37.680
Wanfu.

17:38.440 --> 17:40.320
You must not steal.

17:40.560 --> 17:41.160
I...

17:41.520 --> 17:42.180
Okay, okay.

17:42.240 --> 17:44.760
A person of high ideals doesn't drink stolen water,

17:44.760 --> 17:47.080
and an honest person doesn't accept food handed out in contempt.

17:47.080 --> 17:48.940
This is a basic principle of life.

17:49.120 --> 17:50.920
You are not a hired hand of our family,

17:50.920 --> 17:51.960
nor a coolie.

17:52.280 --> 17:54.080
I won't let you work for nothing.

17:54.400 --> 17:55.360
After you drop us off

17:55.360 --> 17:56.840
at the concession later,

17:57.360 --> 17:58.600
I order you

17:58.920 --> 18:00.880
to return this cart.

18:01.280 --> 18:04.040
Then I'll buy you a ticket to Wuhan.

18:04.360 --> 18:06.880
From then on, we'll be even.

18:07.360 --> 18:08.560
You're on your own.

18:08.840 --> 18:09.720
Fine.

18:09.960 --> 18:11.000
We'll be even.

18:11.240 --> 18:11.900
But Master,

18:12.200 --> 18:13.800
remember what you just said.

18:16.200 --> 18:17.120
Let's go.

18:18.360 --> 18:19.160
Be careful.

18:41.720 --> 18:42.600
Let's go.

18:43.320 --> 18:44.440
Go.

18:46.960 --> 18:48.920
You also know fear when the house collapsed.

18:48.920 --> 18:50.680
Your whole family are gentlemen,

18:50.680 --> 18:51.810
and I'm the villain.

18:51.920 --> 18:53.400
Since I'm such a villain helping you with your luggage,

18:53.400 --> 18:55.600
carry it yourselves if you're capable.

18:55.680 --> 18:57.440
Why are you rambling?

18:58.080 --> 18:59.410
Chengtuo, don't speak.

18:59.480 --> 19:00.400
Rambling.

19:28.080 --> 19:29.210
Don't get any ideas.

19:29.320 --> 19:30.360
There are checkpoints outside.

19:30.360 --> 19:31.080
If you dare to run,

19:31.080 --> 19:32.240
I'll shoot you.

20:57.120 --> 20:59.160
Get up.

21:02.760 --> 21:03.920
Get up.

21:04.240 --> 21:05.160
When will this gate open?

21:05.160 --> 21:05.640
Do you know what China

21:05.640 --> 21:06.640
is like right now?

21:06.880 --> 21:08.740
It's useless telling me all this.

21:13.160 --> 21:13.800
Grandpa.

21:13.840 --> 21:15.120
Right here.

21:17.040 --> 21:17.840
We're here.

21:27.120 --> 21:28.040
Be careful.

21:28.840 --> 21:29.160
Excuse me,

21:29.160 --> 21:30.600
coming through.

21:30.680 --> 21:31.120
Thank you.

21:31.120 --> 21:32.580
Do you know how cruel it is?

21:34.960 --> 21:37.120
Grandpa, let's go up front and see.

21:37.480 --> 21:39.280
Madam, have a rest.

21:39.280 --> 21:39.960
Let's go.

21:40.280 --> 21:41.560
Excuse me, coming through.

21:41.560 --> 21:42.960
Thank you.

21:42.960 --> 21:43.890
Coming through.

21:44.000 --> 21:44.920
Grandpa, slow down.

21:44.920 --> 21:45.880
Come, coming through.

21:45.880 --> 21:47.560
The gate will open when it's supposed to.

21:47.560 --> 21:49.840
If it doesn't open, staying here for a year won't help.

21:49.840 --> 21:51.480
Coming through. Mind the oil.

21:51.480 --> 21:52.600
Coming through. Thank you.

21:52.600 --> 21:53.200
Thank you.

21:53.240 --> 21:54.240
Come on, Grandpa.

21:54.440 --> 21:55.360
Officer,

21:56.000 --> 21:57.680
we have a proper property

21:57.800 --> 21:59.080
in the Concession.

21:59.600 --> 22:00.720
No. 8, Jurenli.

22:01.120 --> 22:01.280
We...

22:01.280 --> 22:02.560
Step back. Step back.

22:02.840 --> 22:03.880
I hear this

22:04.160 --> 22:05.490
hundreds of times a day.

22:06.000 --> 22:07.520
No, you misunderstood.

22:07.520 --> 22:08.440
Look.

22:12.240 --> 22:13.680
This is our title deed.

22:14.000 --> 22:15.800
We are going back to our own home.

22:16.360 --> 22:18.000
Please open the gate and let us in.

22:18.000 --> 22:18.880
If I let you in

22:18.880 --> 22:20.320
just because you have a title deed,

22:20.320 --> 22:21.520
there are over 500 people over there

22:21.520 --> 22:22.240
who all have title deeds.

22:22.240 --> 22:22.520
This...

22:22.520 --> 22:24.240
Should I let them all in?

22:24.960 --> 22:27.160
That... that's unreasonable.

22:27.360 --> 22:28.240
Unreasonable?

22:28.320 --> 22:29.920
This is the French Concession.

22:29.920 --> 22:31.050
They make the rules.

22:31.600 --> 22:32.480
What?

22:32.800 --> 22:33.960
What kind of logic is that?

22:33.960 --> 22:34.560
Exactly.

22:34.560 --> 22:36.840
Isn't this the tail wagging the dog?

22:37.240 --> 22:38.400
Are you Chinese?

22:38.800 --> 22:39.330
Exactly.

22:39.360 --> 22:40.920
You're just a watchdog.

22:42.040 --> 22:42.970
What did you say?

22:43.080 --> 22:44.480
Who are you calling a dog?

22:47.880 --> 22:49.600
Watch out!

22:51.000 --> 22:51.960
It's fine.

22:53.240 --> 22:54.200
Who are you insulting?

22:54.200 --> 22:55.120
I'm insulting you! What about it?

22:55.120 --> 22:56.920
Get out of the way! Open the gate!

23:03.400 --> 23:04.200
Open the gate!

23:04.680 --> 23:05.800
Luggage.

23:06.200 --> 23:07.320
Luggage.

23:08.080 --> 23:09.280
Slow down.

23:09.400 --> 23:11.440
Grandpa, slow down.

23:11.440 --> 23:12.120
Don't push.

23:12.160 --> 23:12.840
Don't push.

23:13.560 --> 23:14.600
Step back.

23:15.480 --> 23:16.610
Give them a warning.

23:20.400 --> 23:21.440
You all saw that.

23:21.760 --> 23:22.880
I'll say it again.

23:23.280 --> 23:25.920
Except for foreigners and those with passes,

23:26.080 --> 23:28.360
if anyone else dares to force their way in,

23:28.360 --> 23:29.640
they'll get a bullet.

23:29.960 --> 23:30.640
Protest!

23:30.800 --> 23:31.640
Protest!

23:32.120 --> 23:34.160
Concession!

23:35.360 --> 23:37.000
The magpie has a nest,

23:37.880 --> 23:39.640
and the dove dwells in it.

23:40.080 --> 23:42.280
This young lady is going to her new home.

23:42.680 --> 23:43.640
Okay, sir.

23:43.840 --> 23:45.080
Even I can't understand it,

23:45.080 --> 23:45.960
let alone them.

23:46.080 --> 23:47.040
Don't be mad at them.

23:47.040 --> 23:48.640
Slaves! Dogs!

23:48.920 --> 23:49.400
Don't be mad at them.

23:49.400 --> 23:49.960
Dogs!

23:50.160 --> 23:51.240
Dogs! Slaves!

23:52.920 --> 23:54.000
Step back!

23:54.920 --> 23:55.520
Back up!

23:55.560 --> 23:56.320
Step back!

23:58.920 --> 24:00.250
National humiliation!

24:00.520 --> 24:02.440
When will they let us in?

24:03.960 --> 24:06.760
I heard they opened it for half an hour the day before yesterday.

24:06.760 --> 24:08.440
Over a thousand people squeezed in.

24:08.440 --> 24:10.480
Later, about ten people were killed,

24:10.480 --> 24:11.810
and then they closed it.

24:12.040 --> 24:12.880
Miss,

24:13.120 --> 24:15.600
I see there are many houses in this concession.

24:15.600 --> 24:17.680
Their back doors all connect to Chinatown, right?

24:17.680 --> 24:19.600
You think others didn't think of this?

24:19.600 --> 24:20.640
The French said,

24:20.960 --> 24:22.720
if anyone dares to let people in through the back door,

24:22.720 --> 24:24.200
they will seal the whole house,

24:24.200 --> 24:25.860
and kick the whole family out.

24:26.160 --> 24:28.320
They're afraid people will take money and secretly let people in.

24:28.320 --> 24:28.960
Look,

24:29.400 --> 24:32.120
all the doors on the street are nailed shut.

24:34.920 --> 24:35.760
Sir,

24:35.880 --> 24:37.340
I think for the time being,

24:37.360 --> 24:38.400
we can't get in.

24:39.120 --> 24:40.920
Why don't we let Madam rest a bit?

24:41.240 --> 24:41.800
Right.

24:42.240 --> 24:43.680
Yujiao, take a rest.

24:45.720 --> 24:46.800
Have a seat.

24:47.760 --> 24:48.360
Step back!

24:48.400 --> 24:49.560
Stay away from the gate! Step back!

24:49.560 --> 24:50.800
Step back!

24:53.000 --> 24:53.600
Protest!

24:53.760 --> 24:55.620
Have something to eat first, sir.

24:56.040 --> 24:56.920
I won't eat.

25:01.000 --> 25:01.800
Eat.

25:02.160 --> 25:03.920
Eat well so we can fight them.

25:15.160 --> 25:16.920
Mom, I'm hungry.

25:28.840 --> 25:29.920
Thank you.

25:32.800 --> 25:35.000
Slaves! Dogs!

25:36.400 --> 25:37.360
Open the door!

25:38.400 --> 25:39.600
Open the door!

25:44.200 --> 25:45.530
You want to live, right?

25:46.080 --> 25:47.000
Four gold bars.

25:47.520 --> 25:48.880
You might as well just rob us.

25:48.880 --> 25:49.920
What a jerk.

25:49.920 --> 25:50.840
Then just wait.

25:51.240 --> 25:52.570
Who do you think you are?

26:38.720 --> 26:40.400
Look at this world.

26:41.040 --> 26:42.520
It's a living hell.

26:44.120 --> 26:46.040
I can't stand seeing this.

26:47.840 --> 26:49.920
Yes, I heard.

26:49.920 --> 26:52.240
They say you are a very capable person.

26:53.680 --> 26:54.520
Bill, hello.

26:54.640 --> 26:55.560
How are you?

26:55.760 --> 26:56.440
Hello, sir.

26:56.440 --> 26:57.920
Good.

27:08.400 --> 27:09.600
One person,

27:10.200 --> 27:11.360
four bars.

27:15.800 --> 27:17.720
Can you make it cheaper?

27:21.520 --> 27:22.960
Four bars it is.

27:46.600 --> 27:47.680
Here are two.

27:48.800 --> 27:50.720
A deposit.

27:59.400 --> 28:01.920
Wait for me here at ten o'clock tonight.

28:01.920 --> 28:03.000
Remember,

28:03.080 --> 28:04.440
don't let anyone know.

28:04.440 --> 28:05.440
Okay.

28:06.040 --> 28:07.000
Got it.

28:09.600 --> 28:11.000
What will we do in the future?

28:11.000 --> 28:12.760
Let's get into the Concession first.

28:12.760 --> 28:13.560
Hurry up.

28:22.040 --> 28:23.800
An imported woolen coat.

28:24.720 --> 28:25.680
Looks nice.

28:26.280 --> 28:27.240
Kid,

28:28.320 --> 28:29.800
you know your stuff.

28:30.520 --> 28:31.800
What do you want?

28:33.600 --> 28:34.760
What do I want?

28:35.240 --> 28:36.720
It's what do you want.

28:38.120 --> 28:39.560
An inside job.

28:45.960 --> 28:48.360
If you want to keep my mouth shut,

28:48.360 --> 28:49.760
it's easy.

28:50.160 --> 28:51.760
Tonight,

28:52.560 --> 28:54.680
get four people inside for me.

28:57.560 --> 28:59.360
I won't let you do it for nothing.

28:59.880 --> 29:01.480
I'll give you two gold bars.

29:03.800 --> 29:05.200
Do you believe

29:05.760 --> 29:08.200
I'll report you to the French Municipal Council?

29:08.200 --> 29:09.920
Jean Paul from the Council

29:09.920 --> 29:10.920
is my brother.

29:11.160 --> 29:13.120
We are sworn brothers.

29:13.120 --> 29:15.080
Get out of here, you little brat!

29:16.480 --> 29:18.280
I'll report you to the Japanese.

29:24.280 --> 29:25.400
The Japanese?

29:25.960 --> 29:27.240
The Japanese bullets

29:27.240 --> 29:28.520
have no eyes.

29:38.440 --> 29:40.800
I'll shoot you, you little brat!

29:41.200 --> 29:43.720
I am a living Buddha here.

29:44.120 --> 29:45.840
Look at that gate.

29:45.840 --> 29:47.520
Every time it opens and closes,

29:47.520 --> 29:49.440
how many Chinese have I saved?

29:51.640 --> 29:53.280
You little brat.

29:56.760 --> 29:57.280
Brother.

29:57.280 --> 29:58.520
No.

29:58.960 --> 30:00.080
Living Buddha.

30:00.080 --> 30:00.480
Look,

30:00.480 --> 30:01.640
it's my fault.

30:01.640 --> 30:03.800
I failed to recognize a great man.

30:04.360 --> 30:05.820
Are you going to report me?

30:05.960 --> 30:06.720
Me?

30:06.840 --> 30:07.920
What would I report?

30:07.920 --> 30:09.880
I was blind.

30:11.920 --> 30:12.840
Brother, look.

30:14.080 --> 30:16.120
Zhang Renkui is my master.

30:16.280 --> 30:18.280
Please do me a favor for his sake.

30:18.920 --> 30:23.880
Shanghai Yuankui is your master?

30:24.240 --> 30:26.560
We are both from Zaozhuang.

30:32.920 --> 30:33.920
Kid,

30:34.480 --> 30:37.160
aren't you afraid of biting your tongue?

30:39.600 --> 30:40.460
Living Buddha,

30:40.600 --> 30:42.520
I am a refugee here.

30:42.520 --> 30:43.120
Me,

30:44.120 --> 30:45.160
my father,

30:45.160 --> 30:46.520
my wife, and my nanny

30:46.520 --> 30:48.120
are all waiting there.

30:48.120 --> 30:50.080
I really have no other choice.

30:50.080 --> 30:51.240
My business is gone.

30:51.400 --> 30:53.080
My wife is pregnant.

30:53.080 --> 30:55.120
In this world, money is nothing.

30:55.120 --> 30:57.180
Only when you are alive is there hope.

30:58.040 --> 30:59.760
Brother, Living Buddha, I beg you.

30:59.760 --> 31:00.280
Tonight,

31:00.280 --> 31:01.960
get the four of us inside.

31:01.960 --> 31:02.640
Please.

31:02.960 --> 31:04.290
According to the rules.

31:04.360 --> 31:06.360
It is what it is.

31:07.640 --> 31:08.970
According to the rules.

31:10.440 --> 31:11.400
One person,

31:12.800 --> 31:13.760
four bars.

31:14.120 --> 31:16.680
Not one less.

31:16.680 --> 31:17.840
If you have the bars,

31:17.840 --> 31:19.440
at 10:00 p.m.,

31:19.560 --> 31:21.320
wait for me here.

32:07.920 --> 32:09.160
Yueming,

32:09.560 --> 32:10.920
when our family

32:10.920 --> 32:13.440
was wandering in Shanghai,

32:13.960 --> 32:16.320
the Battle of Nanjing, 700 miles away,

32:16.320 --> 32:18.400
had reached its final moment.

32:19.400 --> 32:22.040
Due to the sheer disparity in strength between the enemy and us,

32:22.040 --> 32:24.720
the Nationalist Government's strategic decisions were seriously flawed

32:24.720 --> 32:26.120
and wavering.

32:26.520 --> 32:29.600
Furthermore, due to the extreme chaos in the command system,

32:29.600 --> 32:31.360
the defense of Nanjing

32:31.520 --> 32:33.280
collapsed rapidly.

33:10.680 --> 33:12.680
Commander Liao sent me to let you go.

33:13.040 --> 33:14.480
What's the situation outside?

33:14.480 --> 33:16.210
Zhonghua Gate is about to fall.

33:16.240 --> 33:18.840
That guy Tang Shengzhi retreated first himself.

33:18.840 --> 33:19.920
It's a complete mess now.

33:19.920 --> 33:21.450
Some retreat, some defend.

33:21.560 --> 33:22.400
Generals can't find soldiers,

33:22.400 --> 33:23.920
and soldiers can't find generals.

33:23.920 --> 33:25.840
They've all become headless flies.

33:25.840 --> 33:27.360
It was expected.

33:31.760 --> 33:32.800
Tell me about it.

33:32.800 --> 33:34.480
Going to Yijiang Gate in the north

33:34.480 --> 33:35.240
is the only way to survive.

33:35.240 --> 33:36.240
Run quickly.

34:35.000 --> 34:36.040
Don't push.

34:36.040 --> 34:36.639
Alright.

34:37.760 --> 34:38.360
Step back.

34:38.480 --> 34:40.280
Step back.

34:40.760 --> 34:41.360
Step back.

34:44.600 --> 34:45.560
Don't push.

34:58.800 --> 35:00.130
Brother, don't do this.

35:01.160 --> 35:02.290
The gun might go off.

35:02.600 --> 35:03.960
Good to know.

35:05.040 --> 35:06.360
This gown is nice.

35:06.440 --> 35:07.770
You look like a rich man.

35:08.040 --> 35:09.880
You must have silver coins on you.

35:09.880 --> 35:10.840
Don't move.

35:11.160 --> 35:12.160
I'll do it myself.

35:15.280 --> 35:16.880
Don't move. Put the gun down.

35:18.360 --> 35:19.290
Put the gun down.

35:20.320 --> 35:21.200
Don't move. Put the gun down.

35:21.200 --> 35:21.880
Don't move.

35:24.680 --> 35:25.520
Put it down.

35:26.000 --> 35:27.000
Put the gun down.

35:27.160 --> 35:28.000
Put it down.

35:30.000 --> 35:30.840
Everyone,

35:31.440 --> 35:32.680
I'll count to three.

35:33.240 --> 35:34.560
Put your guns down.

35:34.960 --> 35:37.840
Whoever doesn't is a coward.

35:39.640 --> 35:40.960
One.

35:43.000 --> 35:44.200
Two.

35:46.400 --> 35:47.120
Three.

35:51.760 --> 35:52.480
Don't move.

35:52.480 --> 35:54.560
Don't move.

36:08.000 --> 36:09.000
Don't move.

36:09.000 --> 36:10.080
If the gun goes off,

36:10.360 --> 36:12.440
your brains will splatter all over.

36:22.880 --> 36:24.200
You are a deserter.

36:25.440 --> 36:26.770
With a battle like this,

36:27.080 --> 36:29.640
the regiment and brigade commanders are missing,

36:29.640 --> 36:31.720
and we don't know where the positions are.

36:31.720 --> 36:33.720
If I'm not a deserter, should I be cannon fodder?

36:33.720 --> 36:35.380
I see you are a martial artist.

36:35.880 --> 36:37.320
You are also a soldier.

36:48.280 --> 36:49.000
Outside,

36:50.000 --> 36:52.080
the Japanese are bombing the Chinese.

36:52.080 --> 36:53.200
Inside,

36:53.520 --> 36:54.840
let's not point our guns

36:54.840 --> 36:56.000
at each other.

37:14.040 --> 37:15.160
Put it down.

37:20.160 --> 37:21.600
Put it down.

37:26.440 --> 37:28.280
There's a cave-in. Run!

37:28.840 --> 37:29.720
Don't push.

37:31.320 --> 37:32.040
Don't push.

37:32.760 --> 37:33.880
Where are you running?

37:33.880 --> 37:34.880
Guanghua Gate.

37:35.040 --> 37:35.840
Don't push.

37:36.040 --> 37:37.000
The enemies are attacking from

37:37.000 --> 37:37.920
the east, west, and south.

37:37.920 --> 37:40.520
If you want to live, head north to Yijiang Gate.

37:49.720 --> 37:51.360
Brother, which way should we run?

37:51.360 --> 37:52.400
Follow him.

37:52.800 --> 37:53.520
Let's go.

38:28.680 --> 38:29.920
Help us.

38:30.480 --> 38:31.840
Save the kids.

38:32.720 --> 38:34.200
Help us.

38:34.880 --> 38:36.200
Help us.

38:36.560 --> 38:38.120
Save the kids.

38:39.120 --> 38:40.600
Save the kids.

38:41.000 --> 38:42.400
Help us.

38:42.960 --> 38:44.840
Save the kids.

38:45.120 --> 38:45.600
Help us.

38:45.720 --> 38:47.120
Help.

38:47.560 --> 38:48.640
Save the kids.

38:54.040 --> 38:55.120
Help us.

38:55.920 --> 38:57.000
Save the kids.

38:58.360 --> 38:59.480
Help us.

38:59.880 --> 39:00.720
Help us.

39:01.960 --> 39:03.080
Save the kids.

39:08.440 --> 39:09.400
Help.

39:10.840 --> 39:11.880
Save the kids.

39:13.640 --> 39:14.520
Help.

39:19.480 --> 39:20.720
Save the kids.

39:25.160 --> 39:26.200
Damn it.

39:26.800 --> 39:28.080
Help.

39:29.280 --> 39:29.960
Brother.

39:45.240 --> 39:46.600
Pull them out, quick.

39:47.640 --> 39:48.080
Hurry.

39:48.760 --> 39:49.240
Kids.

39:49.320 --> 39:49.760
Hurry.

39:51.360 --> 39:52.400
Get out of here.

39:52.840 --> 39:54.120
Go, kids.

39:57.400 --> 39:58.680
Hurry, go.

40:00.160 --> 40:01.440
Go, hurry.

40:02.720 --> 40:03.680
Come out.

40:04.600 --> 40:05.720
Hurry up.

40:06.880 --> 40:08.080
Is anyone else there?

40:08.240 --> 40:08.800
Let go.

40:08.800 --> 40:10.760
One, two, three.

40:11.360 --> 40:12.520
Go.

40:34.600 --> 40:35.360
Wait for me.

40:36.960 --> 40:38.160
Come here quickly.

40:38.160 --> 40:38.680
Hurry.

40:41.320 --> 40:42.240
It's okay.

40:45.360 --> 40:46.080
Come on.

40:46.920 --> 40:48.280
Just go without me.

40:48.440 --> 40:48.840
Go.

40:48.840 --> 40:50.040
Wait a minute.

40:51.760 --> 40:53.420
Let's go, we're setting sail.

40:57.080 --> 40:58.360
Go, faster.

40:59.200 --> 40:59.960
Don't come over.

40:59.960 --> 41:00.840
No more people.

41:01.200 --> 41:01.760
Wait.

41:01.920 --> 41:02.880
We can't take any more people.

41:02.880 --> 41:04.540
We can't take any more people.

41:06.400 --> 41:07.440
We can't take any more people!

41:07.440 --> 41:08.360
Wait for me!

41:08.680 --> 41:10.040
It's just me.

41:10.480 --> 41:11.810
Can't you wait a moment?

41:18.440 --> 41:19.800
Brother, I'll go first.

41:20.000 --> 41:21.600
I don't want to drag you down.

41:25.200 --> 41:26.130
Are you an idiot?

41:26.360 --> 41:27.760
If I don't bring you back,

41:28.280 --> 41:30.760
how am I supposed to explain it to your sister?

41:30.760 --> 41:33.220
I only have one leg, how can I cross the river?

41:34.000 --> 41:35.800
I'll just drag you down to death.

41:35.920 --> 41:38.440
Even if I have to carry you, I'll get you across.

41:38.440 --> 41:39.100
Stay alive.

41:39.200 --> 41:40.400
You stay alive for me.

41:40.480 --> 41:41.520
Do you hear me?

41:42.280 --> 41:43.320
That bastard.

41:43.680 --> 41:45.000
He ran away by himself.

41:45.760 --> 41:46.880
What a scumbag.

41:48.040 --> 41:49.840
Why are you just standing there?

41:51.320 --> 41:53.040
Doesn't this thing smell a bit too much?

41:53.040 --> 41:54.400
You might as well have found a coffin.

41:54.400 --> 41:56.040
You want to live, who cares about the smell?

41:56.040 --> 41:57.300
Take off your clothes.

41:57.800 --> 41:58.680
Take them off.

41:58.880 --> 42:00.540
Take off your clothes, hurry.

42:02.160 --> 42:03.320
Stop dawdling.

42:08.680 --> 42:10.480
This liquor was meant for cleaning your wound.

42:10.480 --> 42:11.740
Have a sip to keep warm.

42:11.920 --> 42:12.960
Hurry.

42:15.600 --> 42:16.880
Leave a sip for him.

42:24.080 --> 42:24.760
Okay?

42:37.560 --> 42:39.760
Here, take a sip to warm up.

42:41.840 --> 42:42.880
Hold on tight!

42:47.080 --> 42:47.840
Alright.

42:48.880 --> 42:49.800
Let's go.
